    <h2>Why Choose Busy Foods:</h2>
    <br>
    <p>Busy Foods is an easy and safe way to order your favourite food online. With millions of seletions, Busy Foods is the perfect
        place to order almost any food you want. Also, Busy Foods gives you the choice of almost any restaurant you like. Busy Foods
        provides you with 24 hour service all 7 days of the week making it a convenient and reliable source of food, no matter where you are
        and when you need it, Busy Foods will be there. Literally, Busy Foods serves in every country in the world. After all we are 
        made to suit your Busy and on the go lives </p>
        
    <br>
    <hr>
        <h2>Why Create an Account:</h2>
    <br>
    <p>Busy Foods is always trying to get you special offers and cheaper prices for your favourite foods. By creating an account you
        allow us to do just that! By registering for Busy Foods we can provide you with more special offers, to get you, your favourite
        foods, at a cheaper price. Plus every time you order a meal that is $20 or more, you get points. Not just any points, but Busy Foods
        points! These points allow you to buy free meals when you have enough points. They give you the ability to get free meals wherever
        you are and whenever you need. Double plus, by creating an account with us, you are making your life SOOO much easier. This allows 
        you to quickly just go to your account and choose your favourite meals, as you can personalize the restaurants and meals that
        are you favourite. So, just by creating an account you get, not a double win, but a TRIPLE WIN! And the question in the heading should
        not be "Why create an account", at this point, it should be "Why not create an account".</p>
        
    <br>
    <hr>
